quoteLast: The citizen has, therefore, spent practically two days to make the trip. By bus he can make the round trip the same day--leave Wahoo 9:10 A.M.; arrive Omaha 11:30 A.M.; leave Omaha 2:00 P.M. and arrive back home at 4:20 P.M.; or he can have still more time in the city by leaving at 5:10 and arriving home at 7:30 P.M.
